{"tid":2455977,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【最新全球金融中心指數報告 香港再上升 1 位排名第4】","createTime":"2021-03-21T14:14:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T14:51:41.000Z","uid":384880,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8bca4d0709ba29e6d958cbfc1b7f94cabab196a1","tid":2455977,"uid":384880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T14:14:33.000Z","msg":"【最新全球金融中心指數報告 香港再上升 1 位排名第4】<br />\n<br />\n最新一期的全球金融中心指數報告今天出爐！繼去年9月後，香港的排名再次攀升一位，於第 29 期全球金融中心指數（GFCI）中整體排名第4。<br />\n<br />\n全球金融中心指數自2007年起持續對全球主要金融中心進行競爭力評估和排名。#Chris局長 於今天的指數發布會上談到即使面對著疫情帶來的挑戰和不確定性，香港金融市場仍然保持堅韌穩健和靈活變通。過去香港一直位居世界金融中心排名首幾位，未來我們亦會持續以各項措施鞏固香港作為頂尖全球金融中心的地位。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q36pny5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ36pny5.jpg&h=0e3cc291&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWikipedia:<br />\n全球金融中心指數（英語：Global Financial Centres Index，簡稱GFCI）是全球金融中心城市競爭力的評價指數，由英國智庫機構Z/Yen和<span class=\"x-small\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"gold\">中國深圳的中國發展研究所</span></strong></span></span>每年頒佈兩次。 該指數被廣泛用於全球金融中心的排名。"},{"pid":"4ee4b015527c8f6cf0c045d7cafae4b4f1fdf821","tid":2455977,"uid":125168,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T14:16:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab5ad01811800e59ac2b1f417c10367aac1fab64","tid":2455977,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T14:43:50.000Z","msg":"佢話第一你地梗係要信啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b301c00b239f0e546ecf6bfb78948b1c5cd44d02","tid":2455977,"uid":30868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T14:45:49.000Z","msg":"飛機杯一隻就造到第一啦on9"},{"pid":"52f43552577bf0c82990a4c4d8f03ebe5c235c32","tid":2455977,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b301c00b239f0e546ecf6bfb78948b1c5cd44d02","tid":2455977,"uid":30868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T14:45:49.000Z","msg":"飛機杯一隻就造到第一啦on9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T14:51:41.000Z","msg":"第一 香港<br />\n第二 九龍<br />\n第三 新界<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}